**/*.log
**/Logs/

# Test results
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/

node_modules/
node_modules
dist/
build/

# ============================================================================
# Docker
# ============================================================================
**/.dockerignore
**/docker-compose.override.yml

# ============================================================================
